_sText: Written for gungame mod only, no buy zones. Map Name: gg_nucleus Version: 1.0 Created By: JLM Email: jlm@jmcivor.com Website: http://jmcivor.com/ Written strictly for GunGame. There are no buy zones, bomb zones, weapons or items whatsoever. Version: 1.1 -Added deathfloor to skybox, so if used on a low-G server and you fall off the map, you actually die :P -Added teleporter -Added a few new cover/snipe spots. -Brightened the level up a bit for visibility. My site! Sprays, Maps, Etc.
